================================================================================
DATA SOURCES
================================================================================

Satellite data methodology based on:
- NASA IMERG (Integrated Multi-satellitE Retrievals for GPM)
- NASA SMAP (Soil Moisture Active Passive)
- Google Earth Engine MODIS (Moderate Resolution Imaging Spectroradiometer)

Note: Current implementation uses climate-based simulation.
Real satellite API integration available separately.

